Is the impurity larger or smaller in magnitude,

00:02:07.310 --> 00:02:08.884
in terms of absolute value,

00:02:08.884 --> 00:02:12.484
when the samples are dominated by a single class?

00:02:12.485 --> 00:02:17.955
Second question, is the impurity larger or smaller in magnitude,

00:02:17.955 --> 00:02:19.695
in terms of absolute value,

00:02:19.694 --> 00:02:25.044
when the frequency of each class is more evenly distributed among classes?

